keyMappings:
unmap d

map b Vomnibar.activateBookmarksInNewTab

map y copyCurrentUrl
map p openCopiedUrlInNewTab

map d removeTab
map u restoreTab
# map C createTab
map R reload hard

map h previousTab
map l nextTab
map < moveTabLeft
map > moveTabRight

map <c-h> scrollLeft
map <c-l> scrollRight

map <c-d> scrollPageDown
map <c-u> scrollPageUp
map J scrollPageDown
map K scrollPageUp

map ,p togglePinTab
map <c-`> visitPreviousTab

map s Vomnibar.activate keyword=gs
map t Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
map z Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map O Vomnibar.activateEditUrl
map S Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=gs
map T Vomnibar.activateEditUrlInNewTab

map [ goPrevious
map ] goNext
